ygData.messageBody:
>Message: 8
> Date: Thu, 4 Nov 1999 15:23:23 -0600
> From: James Schuldes <jgs@...>
>Subject: RE: Lev 35 Exit Ramp was: Kith Nerfed!!! Re: Undead dr ops in Kithicor
>
>Since you seem to have a lot of experience <g>...
>
>What is the best way to get out of level 35? I have been level 35 for a
>week now and my group is power leveling away from me. I need to get thru
>this hell level a.s.a.p.! Help!!!
>
>Sylly Songsynger
><Spirit of the Moon>
>Bard of the 35th song
>somewhere on Innoruuk


Go to Cazic, go directly to Cazic, do not pass go, do not collect 200 plat 8). In a
non-hell level (I think 36) I did 4 bubbles in one long evening there. I recommend
the upper zig. You do have to separate from your usual group because of the list
system (at least on Mith Marr) but man the experience is great and the cash and fine
steel are good.

Invis to run up. Chains and battle songs for melee mobs. Pixie strike to interrupt
the casters. Mana song afterwards. And finally levitate to jump right off the top
and float down afterwards ;P. They will love you Sylly.
